title: Rolling Stones - Live in Australia 1973
description:
A long out of print 50 min b&w documentary of the stones downunder in 73. although a few of the songs have been dubbed with studio versions of the music this is still an enjoyable document with some pretty rare interview footage. extras include a few songs from MSG 1969. this is my first upload on the pirate bay. hope all goes well. thanks, -vertigoswirl

there will be many to follow...
